Class FibonacciSeries

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.polsl.tomasz.walorski.model.FibonacciSeries

  • public class FibonacciSeries
extends java.lang.Object
    FibonacciSeries class can to obtain series, using recursive and iterative way. Variable LastValSeries store a value of last element of generated series
